Dark Sentinel 
sleek raven 
roosts in a
dead tree
by silver 
sands,

There is a chill
on the wind
that makes you
pull your collar
tight,

Crow cold
stares its
dark eye pierces
the horizon
out to the far sea,

What does this
Corvid Cassandra
know but will
not reveal ?
